description: In this round of testing Dr. Pierce tries out Rosie MK II human sensory inputs, she responds well. Her “Regenerative Orgasm” function is still online and Dr. Pierce unwisely tests Rosie’s vaginal ducts for proper lubricant flow. Knowing that this prototype has not been cleared for this type of hard use, Rosie’s response to several different positions are also being tested. Rosie Mark II has secured the spot of a favorite prototype…
title: SciFi Dreamgirls Episode: Rosie Mark II - Human Trials
